UART transmit buffer example
text
comp [fifo] .tx:
  width: 8
  length: 64
  :

CPU writes:
text
.tx:{
  push = acc
  set = sendInstruction
}

UART consumes:
text
.tx:{
  pop = uartReady
  set = uartReady
}

The FIFO stores bytes until UART is ready to transmit them.

