CPU Call Stack Example
A simplified return-address stack:
text
comp [stack] .callStack:
  width: 16
  length: 32
  :

CALL:
text
.callStack:{
  push = pc
  set = callInstruction
}

RET:
text
16wire returnAddress =
.callStack:top

.callStack:{
  pop = 1
  set = retInstruction
}

The most recently saved program counter is restored first.

